storyInfo: Penguin Logistics meets Waai Fu and Jaye at an open-air party, where Waai Fu and Texas pair up to vent about their frustrations. Emperor's performance is reaching its climax when he is suddenly slain by the Rat King.

attributes.content: 00:38 A.M. \ Dusty
Downtown Lungmen, Plaza, Outdoor Party
We followed the directions all the way but why is... is that a block party?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Check out that candle! It's huge!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Settle down, Exusiai.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: The air smells so sickly sweet, I feel like I want to puke.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Mmm... we oughta get ourselves a booth here next time. I bet we'd make a bundle!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Texas, have you heard from the boss?
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Not yet. He's probably passed out drunk somewhere.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Exusiai, can you get this thing off my head?
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Why!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Thanks to this stupid light on my head, I don't get to wear big fun party hats like that. I'm so jealous!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: What happens if you try to force a hat on?
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: I get a feeling that's something like waking up hungover to find I'm in the passenger seat of a car driven by a very emotionally charged Texas.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: And that don't sound like a good time.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: So you've tried that before...
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: So where's the boss?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: There's so many people here, if the enemy chases us this way, they'll get all mixed up with the civilians...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Ah.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: It's Penguin Logistics.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: And you're... the girl from the detective agency...
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: And this guy here with you is that infamous knife-wielding helmsman from the docks?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: What? No. That's the craziest version I've heard yet...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I'm just a typical hawker. Oh! Tonight I'm a part-time finball master.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: And you must be Texas?
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Something happened tonight. Don't act like you don't know.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Waai Fu, you don't have to be so aggressive with them. They're just...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: I know. But it's ridiculous how many times this has happened.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: It's fine as long as you don't get anyone else mixed up in this.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: But when it comes to getting innocent people hurt, causing so much damage to their property, can't you think like honest, law-abiding citizens for once?
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: (Nothin' we can say to that.)
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...So what?
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: So we must correct your deficient character.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Th- there's no need to come to blows here. We know we've made a lot of trouble for a lot of people tonight, but we can talk this out.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Sure.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Texas?!
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Let me say this first: everything that's happened tonight is completely baffling and inexplicable, and also completely exhausting.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: So let's just say I'm not in a great mood right now.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: You hear what I'm saying?
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: One on one. If I win, you guys follow the rules to the letter.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: ...for at least one month.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: (Just a month?!)
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: And if I win, then you and all your goldbricking busybodies have to mind your own damned business.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Fair's fair... But I won't go easy on you. Get ready!
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Ugh. How did we come to this.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Hold on! Both of you, calm down! You can't just have a fistfight in the middle of the...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Woah! Kung fu! Sick!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: The wolf's not going down easy. C'mon! Look out behind you!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: It's been a long time since I saw Yan kung fu this good! Show us some more!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: This isn't a show!
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Get her, Texas!
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Watch your leg! It's a feint!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: You don't have to join in!
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Soda. Want some?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: Oh. Thank ya kindly. But ain't ya gonna try to stop this little kerfuffle?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: I can't stop it. Looks like you know that already.
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: So we just watch?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Or I guess we could cheer them on?
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: *crackle*
attributes.name: Broadcast

attributes.content: What's that?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Attention! All good citizens attending the Sauin celebration!
attributes.name: Broadcast

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: What's up? What's that guy doing?
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Can you hear me?
attributes.name: Broadcast

attributes.content: Hey! You're too loud!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Aight. Great. You can hear me.
attributes.name: Broadcast

attributes.content: Now, everybody, quiet down! Quiet down please!
attributes.name: Broadcast

attributes.content: Lend me your ears. And bow before me.
attributes.name: Broadcast

attributes.content: What's this guy's deal?
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Wait a minute, that's Emperor! From Monster Siren Records! C'mon!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Shouldn't he be in Columbia?! What's he doing in Lungmen?
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: What is Mr. Emperor... doing?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: The boss always does this music producer thing.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: I mean, he is a music producer.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Our operating capital ain't just from the logistics business. The baws's got all kinds of revenue streams. Like...
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Like what?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Nah. Never mind. Prob'ly best not to say too much.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Grr!
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: What's the matter? You're slowing down.
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Look how the people are moving around us. It's too regimented. Something's not right.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Don't make excuses!
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: EM! PER! OR!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: EM! PER! OR!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: ...how noisy.
Today is Sauin, Mr. Emperor, but your dreadful 'music' is loud enough to wake the dead.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Say what?!
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: You... when did... how'd you get behind me...?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Good night, Mr. Emperor. And a happy Sauin to you.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: ...ugly ass rat, you better... remember...
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: What just happened? Is this some kind of play...?
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Did he just stab Emperor? Is he dead?!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Hya!
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Hai-ya!
attributes.name: Waai Fu

attributes.content: Urk...!
attributes.name: Drunk

attributes.content: Hey, Waai Fu, you hit the wrong...
attributes.name: Jaye

attributes.content: No. She didn't.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: We're surrounded.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Um... Did they follow us all the way from the slums?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: All these fellers here, they're all on the same team?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: No way. So many...
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: They're all here for us. It was a trap. And Mr. Emperor...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: *Gasp!*
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Is this thing on...? Ahem, hello? Testing? People of Lungmen, good evening.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Please do not panic. This dead fellow here is but an insignificant penguin. The Sauin celebrations will proceed as planned. Naturally, some professionals will be here shortly to remove this bothersome corpse.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Now I know this is quite sudden, and I apologize for the interruption, but I thought I would add one more special program to tonight's Carnival.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Our friends from Siracusa have brought us a very special gift. It is hidden somewhere here in this very Carnival.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: Time grows short, my friends.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: (Is he watching me? No, wait, that old man...)
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: It will be terrible if no one finds this precious treasure.
attributes.name: Rat King

attributes.content: The very last surprise of your lives.
attributes.name: Rat King
